title: Quarantine Check-In #10 👨🏻‍⚕️
description:
This week in the Quar, the guys check in with Dr. Dave to see what’s safe to do during this time (can Grandma get her hair done?) A fun time in the Berkshires is had during Memorial Day Weekend, and Christian invents the ‘pickle-tini’ aka a martini using Bob’s Pickle Pops.
